      <title>台湾倒下对我们来说将是“灾难”，特朗普选择科尔比说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/fall-of-taiwan-would-be-disaster-for-us-nominee-colby-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·科尔比（Elbridge Colby）总统在参议院确认听证会上说，台湾跌至中国“将是美国利益的灾难”，该岛政府必须筹集国防支出来阻止北京。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/fall-of-taiwan-would-be-disaster-for-us-nominee-colby-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 18:40:54 GMT</pubDate>
